metatags.og:title: What can you do to help us process your return more smoothly? | Virginia Tax
metatags.og:description: Steps you can take to reduce the chances that your return will be stopped for review (and delay your refund):  Be sure you have all W-2s, 1099s, and other withholding information before filing your return. Don’t rely on year-end pay stub information – it may not match what your employer reports to us.  Include your Virginia driver’s license or Virginia identification card number on your return.
